flowRoot.flowPara: Life is all about balance. Work and play. Business and family. Rest and exercise. Not too much and not too little. It's especially true with your body. At Balance Chiropractic of Green Bay our goal is to help you achieve balance of your spine and nervous system. This symmetry helps your body communicate, function and move at its optimum.

Dr. Andrew Kiefert, CEO of Balance Chiropractic, believes that every patient should be treated as an individual and cared for like they are a part of his family. Care is specialized to fit each patient with careful consideration in helping you meet your unique health care goals. Dr. Andy cares for patients of all ages and has certification in caring for pregnant women.

Balance Chiropractic is located within The CLINIC at Fitnessology. Here, personalized Chiropractic is combined with world class personal training, neuromuscular therapy and massage therapy. We expect and achieve the highest results.
